#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:2
#: 190d2ccdbb4e4dc092f134b9666ea4f0
msgid "Diffusion"
msgstr "扩散"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:4
#: 3477a4cc53694760a7b96093e55bb8ed
msgid ""
"Two transient problems in ``examples/diffusion/``: a linear heat equation "
"with implicit Euler time stepping (``heat/heat.py``) and a nonlinear phase-"
"field problem solved by Newton's method at each timestep (``allen-cahn/``). "
"Together they exercise both the linear time-stepping pattern from "
":doc:`../user_guide/time_integration` and the nonlinear / Newton pattern "
"from :doc:`../user_guide/linear_solvers`. The Allen-Cahn problem ships in "
"three flavours: the hand-written backward-Euler Newton loop (``ac.py``), the"
" same step driven by ``torch_sla.nonlinear_solve`` (``ac_torch_sla.py``), "
"and an unconditionally energy-stable convex–concave splitting "
"(``ac_convex_concave.py``)."
msgstr ""
"``examples/diffusion/`` 中的两个瞬态问题:采用隐式 Euler "
"时间步进的线性热方程(``heat/heat.py``),以及每个时间步用牛顿法求解的非线性相场问题(``allen-"
"cahn/``)。二者一起演练了来自 :doc:`../user_guide/time_integration` 的线性时间步进模式,以及来自 "
":doc:`../user_guide/linear_solvers` 的非线性 / 牛顿模式。Allen-Cahn 问题提供三种风味:手写的后向 "
"Euler 牛顿循环(``ac.py``)、把同一步交给 ``torch_sla.nonlinear_solve`` "
"驱动(``ac_torch_sla.py``),以及无条件能量稳定的凸-凹分裂(``ac_convex_concave.py``)。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:19
#: 3386b4e24fbf40a181fbb266465bb39a
msgid "2D heat equation — ``heat/heat.py``"
msgstr "二维热方程——``heat/heat.py``"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:21
#: b8dcbc4804b0488b83c43a9d74ded032
msgid "The strong form is"
msgstr "强形式为"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:23
#: a2674071ac774943b06bbdfef25aec69
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"u_t \\;=\\; D^2\\, \\Delta u\n"
"\\quad \\text{in } \\Omega,\n"
"\\qquad u = 0 \\text{ on } \\partial\\Omega,"
msgstr ""
"u_t \\;=\\; D^2\\, \\Delta u\n"
"\\quad \\text{in } \\Omega,\n"
"\\qquad u = 0 \\text{ on } \\partial\\Omega,"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:29
#: eef770b19ec540789e2c8b877c1c3b93
msgid ""
"on the unit square with a multi-frequency Fourier-series initial condition "
"from :class:`~tensormesh.dataset.HeatMultiFrequency`."
msgstr ""
"在单位正方形上，初始条件取自 :class:`~tensormesh.dataset.HeatMultiFrequency` 的多频傅里叶级数。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:33
#: 9200a954ab694a8bbce43ecbfc4f9820
msgid "Backward (implicit) Euler turns each step into a linear solve:"
msgstr "后向（隐式）Euler 将每一步都转化为一个线性求解："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:35
#: 3561c1fc370d4e14a894ab4a012d1bef
#, python-brace-format
msgid "(M + \\Delta t\\, D^2\\, A)\\, U^{n+1} \\;=\\; M\\, U^{n},"
msgstr "(M + \\Delta t\\, D^2\\, A)\\, U^{n+1} \\;=\\; M\\, U^{n},"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:39
#: f0562c073aff400b9b5d48312f1a988f
msgid ""
"where :math:`M` is the mass matrix and :math:`A` is the Laplace stiffness. "
"The script assembles both once and reuses them across steps:"
msgstr "其中 :math:`M` 是质量矩阵，\\ :math:`A` 是拉普拉斯刚度。脚本将两者各装配一次，并在各步之间重复使用："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:43
#: b85a684c771b45e5971aa34e85c4cc25
msgid "examples/diffusion/heat/heat.py"
msgstr "examples/diffusion/heat/heat.py"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:72
#: 2a3151c686024f2cafa813985cc0803a
msgid "A few choices reflect the user-guide patterns:"
msgstr "其中有几处选择体现了用户指南中的模式："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:74
#: e290fecdd4a14f1ebe16e19bb9c26cff
msgid ""
"**Quadratic triangles** (``order=2, element_type=\"tri\"``) — heat diffusion"
" is smooth on the interior, so order-2 elements give a much sharper match to"
" the analytical solution at the same mesh size."
msgstr ""
"**二次三角形**\\ （\\ ``order=2, element_type=\"tri\"``\\ "
"）——热扩散在内部是光滑的，因此在相同网格尺寸下，2 阶单元能与解析解高度吻合得多。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:78
#: c5181605b1384c398f66b41f7ddfcb97
msgid ""
"**One assembly, many solves.** ``K`` and ``K_`` are built before the loop. "
"Each step only does a matrix-vector ``M @ U``, a condense-RHS, and a solve —"
" so the bulk of the cost is the per-step linear solve."
msgstr ""
"**装配一次，多次求解。** ``K`` 和 ``K_`` 在循环之前构建。每一步只做一次矩阵-向量乘 ``M @ U``\\ "
"、一次右端项凝聚和一次求解——因此大部分开销都在每步的线性求解上。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:82
#: 98d3614f7a9046af93a40477a5594475
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**Comparison with truth.** "
":meth:`~tensormesh.dataset.HeatMultiFrequency.solution` returns the "
"analytical solution at each time, and ``mesh.plot({\"prediction\": Us, "
"\"ground truth\": Us_gt}, save_path=\"heat.mp4\", dt=dt)`` writes a side-by-"
"side animation."
msgstr ""
"**与真值对比。** :meth:`~tensormesh.dataset.HeatMultiFrequency.solution` "
"返回每个时刻的解析解，而 ``mesh.plot({\"prediction\": Us, \"ground truth\": Us_gt}, "
"save_path=\"heat.mp4\", dt=dt)`` 会写出一段并排对比的动画。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:88
#: 74a00d7a841a4415b9f6441611ed5b30
msgid ""
"The same scheme expressed with TensorMesh's "
":class:`~tensormesh.ode.builtin.ImplicitLinearEuler` integrator ships "
"alongside as ``heat/heat_ode.py`` — same problem, with ``Condenser`` wired "
"through the three boundary-condition hooks instead of the manual loop. The "
"two scripts produce identical snapshots to machine precision; "
":doc:`../user_guide/time_integration` walks through the integrator version, "
"and this script is the lower-level \"by hand\" one."
msgstr ""
"用 TensorMesh 的 :class:`~tensormesh.ode.builtin.ImplicitLinearEuler` "
"积分器表达的同一格式，作为 ``heat/heat_ode.py`` 一并提供——同一问题，只是将 ``Condenser`` "
"接入三个边界条件钩子，而非手动循环。两个脚本生成的快照在机器精度内完全一致；\\ "
":doc:`../user_guide/time_integration` 详解了积分器版本，而本脚本则是更底层的“手动”版本。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:104
#: fcb7acea3ffe4151b81585c2d21a408a
msgid ""
"*Output of* ``heat.py``: *FEM prediction (left) vs analytical truth (right) "
"over the time window. The two stay visually identical to the eye, with the "
"maximum nodal error decaying smoothly as the backward-Euler step damps the "
"highest Fourier mode.*"
msgstr ""
"*``heat.py`` 的输出*\\ ：\\ *在时间窗口内有限元预测（左）与解析真值（右）的对比。两者在肉眼看来始终完全相同，随着后向 Euler "
"步阻尼掉最高的傅里叶模态，最大节点误差平滑衰减。*"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:111
#: 8d8b8f75c17c44f78471114e23286ce0
msgid "Allen-Cahn phase field — ``allen-cahn/ac.py``"
msgstr "Allen-Cahn 相场——``allen-cahn/ac.py``"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:113
#: a5f40abfba624ab3b45ab674d9f8ad98
msgid "The Allen-Cahn equation is the textbook nonlinear phase-field model:"
msgstr "Allen-Cahn 方程是教科书中的非线性相场模型："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:116
#: 0cca0bf29bfa4772be6ad2f62e1a1961
msgid "u_t \\;=\\; \\Delta u + \\varepsilon^2\\, u\\, (1 - u^2),"
msgstr "u_t \\;=\\; \\Delta u + \\varepsilon^2\\, u\\, (1 - u^2),"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:120
#: dc1c941dee964a84a28bfe0a38f1af61
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"with natural (no-flux) boundary conditions and a smooth initial condition "
"that evolves toward the binary phases :math:`u \\in \\{-1, 1\\}`. With "
":math:`\\varepsilon = 220` and :math:`\\Delta t = 10^{-6}`, the nonlinearity"
" is stiff enough that an explicit integrator would require infeasibly small "
"steps; the script uses **implicit Euler plus Newton iteration**."
msgstr ""
"采用自然（无通量）边界条件，以及一个向二元相 :math:`u \\in \\{-1, 1\\}` 演化的光滑初始条件。在 "
":math:`\\varepsilon = 220` 和 :math:`\\Delta t = 10^{-6}` "
"下，非线性项足够刚性，以至于显式积分器需要小到不可行的步长；因此脚本采用\\ **隐式 Euler 加牛顿迭代**\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:127
#: a2836655e50d483b9e53dc83dfe5f6f0
msgid "At each time step Newton solves the residual"
msgstr "每个时间步，牛顿法求解残差"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:129
#: 2bdd086a5471437998eaffa6271e32e4
msgid ""
"R(c) \\;=\\;\n"
"\\frac{c - c_\\text{old}}{\\Delta t}\\, v\n"
"\\;+\\; D(c)\\, \\nabla v \\cdot \\nabla c\n"
"\\;-\\; f(c)\\, v\n"
"\\;\\xrightarrow{!}\\; 0,"
msgstr ""
"R(c) \\;=\\;\n"
"\\frac{c - c_\\text{old}}{\\Delta t}\\, v\n"
"\\;+\\; D(c)\\, \\nabla v \\cdot \\nabla c\n"
"\\;-\\; f(c)\\, v\n"
"\\;\\xrightarrow{!}\\; 0,"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:137
#: e6337c83f9294d4ba9677acf20ca04aa
msgid ""
"with Jacobian :math:`K = \\partial R / \\partial c` linearized around the "
"current iterate. Both are written as TensorMesh assemblers so the pattern is"
" the same as a linear solve:"
msgstr ""
"其雅可比矩阵 :math:`K = \\partial R / \\partial c` 围绕当前迭代值线性化。两者都写成 TensorMesh "
"装配器，因此其模式与线性求解相同："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:141
#: c6c55a5bd700412b87e4dfa9a5244182
msgid "examples/diffusion/allen-cahn/ac.py (essence)"
msgstr "examples/diffusion/allen-cahn/ac.py（核心）"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:171
#: 72e53da3e2754609ab5d14354db094f3
msgid "Two things that make this easy to write:"
msgstr "有两点让这段代码易于编写："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:173
#: 27fa92b038674f89ba4b4922998c602a
msgid ""
"**Per-iterate parameters via** ``point_data``. The current iterate ``c`` and"
" the previous timestep's solution ``cold`` are passed by name into both "
"``forward`` methods — exactly the argument-dispatch contract documented in "
":doc:`../user_guide/forms`. There is no per-quadrature-point Python loop."
msgstr ""
"**通过** ``point_data`` **传入逐迭代参数。** 当前迭代值 ``c`` 和上一时间步的解 ``cold`` 按名称传入两个 "
"``forward`` 方法——这正是 :doc:`../user_guide/forms` 中所记载的参数分派约定。这里没有逐求积点的 Python "
"循环。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:179
#: bc74394ddb2340ae96e9d1dad6be77ea
msgid ""
"**Reassemble each iteration.** Because ``K`` depends on ``c`` (through "
"``D(c)``, ``df(c)``), it has to be rebuilt every Newton iteration. That is "
"intentional — assembly is cheap on the GPU, and the alternative (computing "
"analytical Jacobians by hand) would require pages of additional code."
msgstr ""
"**每次迭代重新装配。** 由于 ``K`` 依赖于 ``c``\\ （通过 ``D(c)``\\ 、\\ ``df(c)``\\ "
"），它必须在每次牛顿迭代时重建。这是有意为之——在 GPU 上装配开销很低，而另一种做法（手动计算解析雅可比矩阵）则需要数页额外代码。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:185
#: 800eeb54a80c415f816533221d914ad0
msgid ""
"If you would rather hand the whole step to a packaged driver, ``allen-"
"cahn/ac_torch_sla.py`` solves the *same* problem with ``torch-sla``'s "
"``nonlinear_solve`` (Newton / Picard / Anderson with Armijo line search; see"
" :doc:`../user_guide/linear_solvers`). The per-step ``while`` loop above "
"collapses to one call:"
msgstr ""
"如果你更愿意把整个步骤交给一个封装好的驱动器，\\ ``allen-cahn/ac_torch_sla.py`` 用 ``torch-sla`` 的 "
"``nonlinear_solve``\\ （牛顿 / Picard / Anderson，并带 Armijo 线搜索；参见 "
":doc:`../user_guide/linear_solvers`\\ ）求解\\ *同一*\\ 问题。上面每步的 ``while`` "
"循环会浓缩为一次调用："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:191
#: 65e259cea09a4e369dc95d6f026bbf76
msgid "examples/diffusion/allen-cahn/ac_torch_sla.py (essence)"
msgstr "examples/diffusion/allen-cahn/ac_torch_sla.py（核心）"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:207
#: 04b257455bdb410fb3531e060d3933fa
msgid ""
"Two points worth noting. First, ``nonlinear_solve`` can build the Jacobian "
"by autograd, but here we pass the FEM consistent tangent explicitly as "
"``jacobian_fn`` — it is already assembled, so this is both cheaper and "
"exact. Second, the sign: ``KAssembler`` assembles the *negative* tangent "
":math:`K = -\\partial R/\\partial c`, so ``jacobian_fn`` returns "
"``-K.values`` to hand back the true Jacobian :math:`J`, which "
"``nonlinear_solve`` then steps with :math:`J\\,\\delta u = -R`. The two "
"scripts agree to round-off, and ``nonlinear_solve`` additionally gives a "
"correct adjoint backward through the converged solution."
msgstr ""
"有两点值得注意。第一，\\ ``nonlinear_solve`` 可以用 autograd 构建雅可比矩阵，但这里我们将有限元一致切线显式地作为 "
"``jacobian_fn`` 传入——它已经装配好，因此这样既更省又精确。第二，符号问题：\\ ``KAssembler`` 装配的是\\ *负*\\"
" 切线 :math:`K = -\\partial R/\\partial c`\\ ，因此 ``jacobian_fn`` 返回 "
"``-K.values`` 以交回真正的雅可比矩阵 :math:`J`\\ ，随后 ``nonlinear_solve`` 据此以 "
":math:`J\\,\\delta u = -R` 进行迭代。两个脚本在舍入误差内一致，并且 ``nonlinear_solve`` "
"还能给出穿过收敛解的正确伴随反向传播。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:225
#: a06aef734bb247ec875811f358f4ccb3
msgid ""
"*Output of* ``ac.py``: *the order parameter* :math:`\\varphi` *evolving on "
"the unit square. Starting from random noise it rapidly coarsens into the two"
" equilibrium phases (* :math:`\\varphi=\\pm1` *), with diffuse interfaces of"
" width set by* :math:`\\varepsilon`. *Each frame is one resolved Newton "
"solve.*"
msgstr ""
"*``ac.py`` 的输出*\\ ：\\ *序参量* :math:`\\varphi` "
"*在单位正方形上的演化。从随机噪声出发，它迅速粗化为两个平衡相（* :math:`\\varphi=\\pm1` *），界面呈弥散状，其宽度由* "
":math:`\\varepsilon` *决定。每一帧对应一次收敛的牛顿求解。*"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:233
#: b7a1cec37208441b9ccef00318493d57
msgid "Convex–concave splitting — ``allen-cahn/ac_convex_concave.py``"
msgstr "凸-凹分裂 —— ``allen-cahn/ac_convex_concave.py``"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:235
#: a0b36e2f75924dc49a79e263c4698bfd
msgid ""
"``ac.py`` and ``ac_torch_sla.py`` solve the *same* fully-implicit backward-"
"Euler step and only differ in how the Newton solve is driven. "
"``ac_convex_concave.py`` solves a **different time discretisation**: Eyre's "
"convex splitting. It exploits the fact that Allen-Cahn is the :math:`L^2` "
"gradient flow of the double-well energy"
msgstr ""
"``ac.py`` 和 ``ac_torch_sla.py`` 求解 *相同* 的全隐式后向 Euler 步,只在如何驱动牛顿求解上不同。\\ "
"``ac_convex_concave.py`` 求解一种 **不同的时间离散**:Eyre 凸分裂。它利用了 Allen-Cahn 是双井能量的 "
":math:`L^2` 梯度流这一事实"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:241
#: 7d76fa2aafea484b8412c3a317eb56fa
msgid ""
"E(c) \\;=\\; \\int_\\Omega \\tfrac12\\,|\\nabla c|^2\n"
"         \\;+\\; \\varepsilon^2\\, W(c)\\, d\\Omega,\n"
"\\qquad W(c) = \\tfrac14\\,(c^2 - 1)^2,"
msgstr ""
"E(c) \\;=\\; \\int_\\Omega \\tfrac12\\,|\\nabla c|^2\n"
"         \\;+\\; \\varepsilon^2\\, W(c)\\, d\\Omega,\n"
"\\qquad W(c) = \\tfrac14\\,(c^2 - 1)^2,"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:247
#: fc4714dba8274e49843e09576d2361eb
msgid ""
"whose nonlinear term :math:`W'(c) = c^3 - c` splits into a **convex** part "
":math:`c^3` and a **concave** part :math:`-c`. Taking the convex part "
"implicitly and the concave part explicitly gives"
msgstr ""
"其非线性项 :math:`W'(c) = c^3 - c` 分裂为 **凸** 部分 :math:`c^3` 和 **凹** 部分 "
":math:`-c`\\ 。将凸部分取隐式、凹部分取显式,得到"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:251
#: 8c6545fa44ca4e89aebd27de57f5aaf5
msgid ""
"\\frac{c - c_\\text{old}}{\\Delta t}\n"
"\\;=\\; \\Delta c \\;-\\; \\varepsilon^2\\, c^3 \\;+\\; \\varepsilon^2\\, c_\\text{old}."
msgstr ""
"\\frac{c - c_\\text{old}}{\\Delta t}\n"
"\\;=\\; \\Delta c \\;-\\; \\varepsilon^2\\, c^3 \\;+\\; \\varepsilon^2\\, c_\\text{old}."

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:256
#: 29a12223613442dc9069a2d2ab3acd2a
msgid ""
"This scheme is **unconditionally energy-stable** — it decreases :math:`E` "
"for *any* time-step size — and the per-step Newton system is uniquely "
"solvable independent of :math:`\\Delta t`, so the residual and its tangent "
"are"
msgstr ""
"该格式 **无条件能量稳定** —— 它对 *任意* 时间步长都减少 :math:`E` —— 且每步牛顿系统的唯一可解性与 "
":math:`\\Delta t` 无关,因此残差及其切线为"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:261
#: e39c391bb5914c79bb3f28519fc7ea3e
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"R(c)\\,v &= \\int_\\Omega \\tfrac{1}{\\Delta t}\\,(c - c_\\text{old})\\,v\n"
"         \\;+\\; \\nabla c \\cdot \\nabla v\n"
"         \\;+\\; \\varepsilon^2\\, c^3\\, v\n"
"         \\;-\\; \\varepsilon^2\\, c_\\text{old}\\, v \\; d\\Omega, \\\\\n"
"R'(c)[u]\\,v &= \\int_\\Omega \\tfrac{1}{\\Delta t}\\,u\\,v\n"
"         \\;+\\; \\nabla u \\cdot \\nabla v\n"
"         \\;+\\; 3\\,\\varepsilon^2\\, c^2\\, u\\,v \\; d\\Omega."
msgstr ""
"R(c)\\,v &= \\int_\\Omega \\tfrac{1}{\\Delta t}\\,(c - c_\\text{old})\\,v\n"
"         \\;+\\; \\nabla c \\cdot \\nabla v\n"
"         \\;+\\; \\varepsilon^2\\, c^3\\, v\n"
"         \\;-\\; \\varepsilon^2\\, c_\\text{old}\\, v \\; d\\Omega, \\\\\n"
"R'(c)[u]\\,v &= \\int_\\Omega \\tfrac{1}{\\Delta t}\\,u\\,v\n"
"         \\;+\\; \\nabla u \\cdot \\nabla v\n"
"         \\;+\\; 3\\,\\varepsilon^2\\, c^2\\, u\\,v \\; d\\Omega."

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:271
#: 5716442665c64f1e8ef12ea6de4793a4
msgid ""
"The tangent is symmetric positive-definite (the reaction term "
":math:`3\\varepsilon^2 c^2 \\ge 0` only adds to the diagonal), which is the "
"algebraic reflection of the unconditional stability — there is no step-size "
"limit from the nonlinearity:"
msgstr ""
"该切线是对称正定的(反应项 :math:`3\\varepsilon^2 c^2 \\ge 0` 只往对角线上叠加),这是无条件稳定性在代数上的反映 "
"—— 非线性不带来任何步长限制:"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:276
#: 05e0de8eb2334c838e4342b8263ba036
msgid "examples/diffusion/allen-cahn/ac_convex_concave.py (essence)"
msgstr "examples/diffusion/allen-cahn/ac_convex_concave.py(精要)"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:299
#: 76fd7b55911f4d12880797d8a2ca06be
msgid "Why this is worth a separate script:"
msgstr "为什么值得单列一个脚本:"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:301
#: 0b98f922edda4b5196b83faab5b88ca1
msgid ""
"**Bigger time steps.** The fully-implicit ``ac.py`` is stable but its Newton"
" solve can stall when :math:`\\Delta t` is pushed too far; the convex split "
"stays well-behaved, so ``--dt`` can be raised well beyond the fully-implicit"
" limit while the energy still decays monotonically."
msgstr ""
"**更大的时间步。** 全隐式的 ``ac.py`` 虽稳定,但当 :math:`\\Delta t` "
"推得太远时其牛顿求解可能停滞;凸分裂保持良好,因此 ``--dt`` 可以远超全隐式上限,而能量仍单调衰减。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:306
#: f0b4a4dbc71e4ea4ae8fa18f472e7273
msgid ""
"**Same assembler contract.** Both the residual ``NodeAssembler`` and the "
"SPD-tangent ``ElementAssembler`` read the current iterate ``c`` and the "
"previous step ``cold`` from ``point_data`` — the identical argument-dispatch"
" pattern as ``ac.py``; only the *discretisation* changed, not the API."
msgstr ""
"**相同的装配器约定。** 残差 ``NodeAssembler`` 和 SPD 切线 ``ElementAssembler`` 都从 "
"``point_data`` 读取当前迭代值 ``c`` 和上一步 ``cold`` —— 与 ``ac.py`` 完全相同的参数分派模式;改变的只是 "
"*离散格式*,而非 API。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/diffusion.rst:317
#: 6a55b496eb444312997893f6a9fb99c4
msgid ""
"The output animation is written to ``Allen-Cahn-convex-concave-dt<dt>.mp4`` "
"(the file name encodes the ``--dt`` used, so runs at different step sizes do"
" not overwrite each other)."
msgstr ""
"输出动画写入 ``Allen-Cahn-convex-concave-dt<dt>.mp4``(文件名编码了所用的 "
"``--dt``,因此不同步长的运行不会相互覆盖)。"

